Friends:

Please remember that this is a JUnit mailing list and that while we are
qualified to answer questions on JUnit, we are not necessarily Ant
experts. I strongly suggest that you post Ant questions to the Ant user
mailing list in order to get the best possible answers. Now I'm not
saying, "Get those Ant questions the hell out of here"; but I am saying
that you should not expect Ant experts on this list -- it's likely in
your best interests to post your Ant questions to the Ant list.

Thanks.
